@@TJvExecute
Description:
This component let you launch an Application easily and even to wait for his end

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvExecute.Exec@string@string@string
Description:
This will launch the Application with specified parameters and directory

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvExecute.ExecuteAndWait@string@Integer
Description:
This will launch the Application and will wait for his end. Visibility can be WS_HIDE,WS_SHOW,...

